      "writtenOn": "2018-10-17T19:49:22Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Yes, but we still have the restriction going the other direction, ie. the service account still has to be given the rights it actually tries to exercise.  In this case, we\u0027d need to whitelist individual scopes in the LUCI token server config, requiring an update and push every time they changed.  It seemed far simpler to use the already-whitelisted CloudPlatform scope and just rely on the fact that we only actually grant the necessary accesses to our service accounts.",
      "parentUuid": "1248976f_c4908403",
